snippet.title: Parodius Portable: Parodius MSX Remake PSP 60fps
snippet.description: Best viewed in 60 fps. This is played on the default easy settings with the roulette turned off. This one went less smoothly than I would have liked, but I don't think I could have done too much better, since I'm not that great at shoot em ups in general.
